# Re-initialize the Liconic PLC — sends firmware ST 1900 (re-init) +
# ST 1801 (activate handling) + polls ready. Clears most latched error
# states and silences the 30 s alarm beep.
#
# CAVEAT: this re-homes the carousel. Any plate currently in a cassette
# will stay where it is (no motion), but a plate on the shovel/transfer
# mechanism at the moment of reset can end up in an unexpected state.
# Make sure the transfer tray and shovel are empty before calling.
---
bool success
string message
# Error register values read BEFORE the reset — useful for diagnostics.
# ``error_flag_before`` is PLC register RD 1814 ("1" if an error was
# latched, "0" if not). ``error_code_before`` is RD DM200 (matches the
# HandlingError enum in liconic.constants; e.g. "00008" = GATE_CLOSE_ERROR).
string error_flag_before
string error_code_before
